{"tid":2001134,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（家居健身）掌上壓手肘狂響求救","createTime":"2020-05-04T10:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T14:02:48.000Z","uid":4969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9951ad79d8bfc2e4f10b7ca20b248c154a03ad43","tid":2001134,"uid":4969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:18:06.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n細佬我希望半年後考消防，係依加健身室未開返既情況下只可以係屋企做d簡單既訓練，但係有幾個部分都遇到問題，上網搵過好多網睇但都想問吓巴打絲打有冇相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n175cm 65kg 陸續增磅中<br />\n<br />\n每次熱身有做足，最少都用15分鐘<br />\n1. 掌上壓手肘狂響<br />\n一個月岩岩開始操個時完全冇呢個問題發生，大概半個月之後就開始有一兩下響聲，到依加下下都有，完全唔會痛但好大心理影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又驚長遠會出事<br />\n另外想問冇啞鈴（未買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）有冇簡單既方法有冇增加負重去練胸/臂，1分鐘大概做到35～40下跟住就完全冇力，最少要抖返3～5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 練腹<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bTHnzGSgkqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbTHnzGSgkqk&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1nljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=373c72e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bTHnzGSgkqk</a><br />\n跟條link做，但當做到正常sit-up/第三組（單車式捲腹）呢類用到椎骨位做支點既動作，舊尾龍骨會成日磨擦到覺得痛，發唔到力，係床又好輕鬆，係唔係正常？<br />\n<br />\n3. 深蹲<br />\n每次做完，大髀正面靠內側個組大肌力會漲起差唔多成倍，～15分鐘之後先慢慢消退，呢個情況係今個星期突然發生，係咪正常？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cz31yfs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcz31yfs.png&h=d59dbcb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65ae6b804c0d703b3be737678152c21bf61b0766","tid":2001134,"uid":94613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"標準答案：未睇過你個form 斷唔到症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19a6bbc46b5ee0c2384b9ce009ebafe552fb5df","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"試下做左熱身先"},{"pid":"03977d0744525d89f70407bfa05b1a910ddb1d51","tid":2001134,"uid":4969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19a6bbc46b5ee0c2384b9ce009ebafe552fb5df","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"試下做左熱身先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"每次都有做 由頭到腳踭最少10-15分鐘"},{"pid":"6358d4fc75de7e46f65e0e44bd9b3ab688ed566c","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03977d0744525d89f70407bfa05b1a910ddb1d51","tid":2001134,"uid":4969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19a6bbc46b5ee0c2384b9ce009ebafe552fb5df","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"試下做左熱身先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"每次都有做 由頭到腳踭最少10-15分鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"響果個位就多少少"},{"pid":"15a1e6584ea35d4469ad0dd440c7b450b92b725c","tid":2001134,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6358d4fc75de7e46f65e0e44bd9b3ab688ed566c","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03977d0744525d89f70407bfa05b1a910ddb1d51","tid":2001134,"uid":4969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c19a6bbc46b5ee0c2384b9ce009ebafe552fb5df","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"試下做左熱身先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"每次都有做 由頭到腳踭最少10-15分鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"響果個位就多少少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"未斷症就叫佢熱多d身死得仲快wo巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3306b12ca3a002b8e52b4432061055b1553a4cf","tid":2001134,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a1e6584ea35d4469ad0dd440c7b450b92b725c","tid":2001134,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6358d4fc75de7e46f65e0